      "raw_text": "The city council decided last\nnight to postpone for two weeks the\nGreat Northern railways PROPOSE\nton for the elevation of it's tracks\nbetween Division street and Hill\nyard in the Fifth ward. Strong\nopposition has come from that\nward on account of injury to prop\nerty in that section of the city.\n\n\nAt last nights meeting the prop\nerty owners were represented by a\nnumber of lawyers who pointed out\nthe disadvantages of the projected\nchange."
